headline: Is There an Opportunity in ONEOK After Its 32% Share Price Drop in 2025?
summary: If you hold shares of ONEOK, or are on the fence about starting a position, you are probably wondering if the stock’s recent drop is a warning sign or an opportunity. With a year-to-date fall of 32.1% and a one-year dip of 25.1%, ONEOK has been through some testing months. That said, if you zoom out, the picture looks less gloomy. Over the past five years, the stock is actually up an impressive 225%. The question, of course, is where does it go from here? Market headlines have swirled around...
